ValidateItem checks that an item has a non-empty name (delegated to <ref spec="validation.validate_name">validate_name</ref>), a positive quantity (delegated to <ref spec="validation.validate_quantity">validate_quantity</ref>), and a non-negative price (delegated to <ref spec="validation.validate_price">validate_price</ref>). Returns nil if all checks pass; returns a <ref spec="errors.validation_error">ValidationError</ref> describing the first failure otherwise.